\par but can be known to occur after DirectX install completes certain hardware driver updates. 
\par If you do encounter any problems whatsoever after a DirectX installation please refer to the Microsoft Corporation website at \plain\f2\fs20\cf4 http://www.microsoft.com\plain\f2\fs20\cf0  for further details.
