\par \pard\li720\fi-720\plain\lang1033\f2\fs24\b 7.0\tab \plain\f2\fs24\b TROUBLESHOOTING
\par \pard\plain\f2\fs20\b 
\par \plain\f2\fs20 Should you have any difficulties running Worms Armageddon, please check below for common problems and solutions. If you continue to experience difficulties, contact the Team17 support department. As with the majority of entertainment titles that run under Windows\plain\f2\fs20\cf0  \plain\f2\fs20 operating system, you should ensure that you have the maximum amount of system resources available. 
\par \pard\ri-37\plain\f2\fs20 
\par \plain\f2\fs20\cf1\b\i 7.1\tab General Game Information\plain\f2\fs20 
\par 
\par \plain\f2\fs20\cf1\i Recommendations\plain\f2\fs20 
\par \pard\li360\ri-37\fi-360\tx360{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'b7}}\plain\f2\fs20 {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Run Worms Armageddon directly after initialising your system.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Increase your amount of system RAM.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Use a video card that has a minimum of 2Mb RAM and preferably one with 4Mb or more of memory for playing in high detail and high resolution.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Play Worms Armageddon at a lower graphic detail level. There are six detail levels available that defaults to a maximum setting when the game is run initially. This setting can be changed in-game by using the INSERT key.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Ensure that your hard drive has enough free space available should Windows\plain\f2\fs20\cf0  \plain\f2\fs20 need it to create virtual memory.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Use the same sound sample bank for all teams in the game. This will ease the system RAM requirement of the game.
\par \pard\ri-37\plain\f2\fs20 
\par \pard\li360\ri-37\fi-360\tx360{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'b7}}\plain\f2\fs20\cf2 {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Do not install and run the game in compressed partitions if at all possible.
\par \pard\li360\fi-360\tx360{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'b7}}\plain\f2\fs20\cf2 {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Do not run the game in unison with background applications resident. Problems may occur especially with software that puts high demand on system resources or has scheduling options such as disk scanners, disk de-fragmentation programs or virus checkers. It is also advisable if you are running Microsoft Internet Explorer 4 or later that you should disable the active desktop before commencing play.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Do not run the game in unison with background tools resident that either generates a \plain\lang1033\f2\fs20\cf2 toolbar on your Windows desktop or alternatively has an icon on within your Windows taskbar. \plain\f2\fs20\cf2 For example\plain\lang1033\f2\fs20\cf2  if your system has the Microsoft Office toolbar enabled please close this down before commencing play.\plain\f2\fs20\cf2 
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Do not minimise or task-switch during play and quit out of the game should you require access to the full resources available on your system. Worms Armageddon is not designed to run at the same time as other major Windows titles and applications. Continually minimising and task switching between the game and other applications may lead to system problems due to the amount of resources required. 
\par \pard\ri-37\plain\f2\fs20 
\par \plain\f2\fs20\cf1\i Media Care
\par \plain\f2\fs20 CD-ROM discs can be susceptible to producing errors if not correctly taken care of and there are a few steps you may take to minimise these problems:
\par 
\par \pard\li360\ri-37\fi-360\tx360{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'b7}}\plain\f2\fs20 {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Ensure that the CD is not written upon, bent or labelled with stickers.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Handle the CD by the edge to avoid marking the surface with scratches, dirt or dust.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Store the CD in a location that is not prone to extreme heat or humidity.
\par {\pntext\f1\'b7\tab}Store the CD safely in the case provided when not in use to avoid marking the surface with scratches, dirt or dust.
\par \pard\tx0\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\plain\f2\fs20 
